attributes.description: The "TYCHON Endpoint Browser" dashboard provides host visualization data for a single endpoint at a time. The dashboard is a set of several individual views broken down by tabs near the top of the screen. The TYCHON Endpoint Browser â€“ Drives and Disks view displays current Hard Drive and Partitions attached to endpoints at the time TYCHON performed its check.
